  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Altaviva apartments are self-catered and come with a fully equipped kitchen and all the utensils you'll need for you stay. A short walk to resort centre you'll also find a range of restaurants, bars and local supermarkets.</p>
<p>There's a bakery delivery service available which you can pre-book and pay for through reception that includes a range of freshly made foods such as bread and a selection of pastries.</p>
<p>If you don't feel like cooking and would rather be wined and dined, the residence building has it's own restaurant serving continental dishes with views overlooking the ski area. You will need to pre-book through reception and pay locally.</p>
<p>Alternatively, we've partnered up with Huski who provide premium oven ready meals across the French Alps. Huski will deliver your meals directly to your accommodation in time for your arrival, all you'll have to do is cook. If you'd like to know more, please click <a rel="noopener" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/special-offers/huski-food-drink-delivery-service" target="_blank">here</a> for further details.</p>
<p> </p>]]></cateringDescription>
