  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>One bedroom comfort apartments </strong>can sleep up to four people and are 31 - 38m². There's a living room with a two person sofa bed and one twin or double bedroom, and one bathroom.</p>
<p>Some of these apartments have a <strong>special offer</strong> price which are on a first come first served basis.</p>
<p><strong>Two bedroom family apartments </strong>can sleep up to six people and are 41 - 48m². Living room with a two person sofa bed, one twin or double bedroom and a bunk bed room. This apartment has two bathrooms.</p>
<p>Some of these apartments have a <strong>special offer</strong> price which are on a first come first served basis.</p>
<p><strong>Two bedroom comfort apartments </strong>can sleep up to six people and are 40 - 47m². The living room has a two person sofa bed, then two twin or double bedrooms and two bathrooms. </p>
<p><strong>Three bedroom apartments </strong>can sleep up to eight people and are 57 - 58m². Living room has a fireplace and a two person sofa bed. Then two twin or double bedrooms, a third bedroom with either a bunk beds or twin beds and two bathrooms.</p>
<p><strong>Apartment facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Living room with TV</li>
<li>Balcony with mountain views</li>
<li>Kitchenette equipped with ceramic hot plate, dishwasher, microwave oven combi, fridge, kettle, filter coffee maker</li>
<li>Bath with shower head attachment or shower room</li>
<li>Heated towel rails</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Separate WC</li>
<li>Twin or double beds (please specify preference when booking)</li>
<li>Free Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Cleaning kit</li>
<li>Towels and linen</li>
<li>Beds made on arrival (except sofa beds and bunk beds)</li>
<li>End of stay cleaning (except kitchen) is included</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>]]></roomsDescription>
